spamassassin: spamassassin (Spam filter for email
spamassassin:
spamassassin: SpamAssassin provides you with a way to reduce if not completely
spamassassin: eliminate Unsolicited Commercial Email (SPAM) from your incoming
spamassassin: email. It can be invoked by a MDA such as sendmail or postfix, or
spamassassin: can be called from a procmail script, .forward file, etc. It uses a
spamassassin: genetic-algorithm evolved scoring system to identify messages which
spamassassin: look spammy, then adds headers to the message so they can be filtered
spamassassin: by the user's mail reading software.
spamassassin: http://spamassassin.apache.org/
